text:
A couple of suggestions for your grotto when you get back to it.

Podzol (you get this under giant spruce trees) might be good for the bottom of the ponds, you'll need silk touch. 
Moss might also be nice around the waterfall.
Coarse Dirt could be used for a slightly darker texture, you can find it or craft it using 2 dirt and 2 gravel.

Dripleaf might be a good addition but is currently only available in survival from Wandering Traders (I think).
Glow berries could be a good alternative to lanterns, you'll either need to find them in a chest minecart in a new mineshaft or more easily harvest one from the JP server and start growing them.

For the second cave if you want to go for that fairy effect, consider amethyst blocks and clusters.  Clusters can be harvested with silk touch and give off some light.  

Soul lanterns as an alternative light source.

Thanks for the stream good luck with your haunted house!
